{"tid":780262,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"香港男人一生的階段時間表，錯過左返唔到轉頭","createTime":"2018-08-15T04:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T15:16:00.000Z","uid":30006,"like":117,"dislike":168,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"dd971e337524caa510be0bf615e44b1501daf64e","tid":780262,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:46:17.000Z","msg":"1- 20 學習期<br />\n<br />\n20-25 試驗+社會儲exp期<br />\n出黎社會睇下自己有咩優缺點，適合做咩<br />\n<br />\n25 - 30 發奮期<br />\n開始收窄範圍 搵到自己一個成功的 range ，開始朝住呢個 range 努力<br />\n<br />\n30- 35 盡地一煲期<br />\n開始要搵到人生事業的唯一的目標，全力向呢個目標 100% 投放<br />\n<br />\n35-40 收成期<br />\n開始事業有成，如無意外應該有樓有車有家庭，開始由 30-35 種下的事業種子收成<br />\n<br />\n40-50 二度爆上/守業期<br />\n正常黎講如果好彩的話事業步入穩定，初期的高增長開始放緩，呢個時間有人選擇守業，有人選擇再攪第二單大野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上係一個正常男人，非富二代/發達撚的路，當然有人叻仔會推早，但如果你發現你落後有 5 年以上，有可能好難再追<br />\n<br />\n因為你的身體狀況同埋你的交際圈子的性質都不停咁變。<br />\n<br />\n勸下各位巴打真係及早利用你的健康同人際圈做野，唔好成日以為仲有大把時間，你而家做可能身邊的人配合到你，你遲d做可能力不從心 + 無人再幫到你。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncomfort zone 係男人大敵，好多人因為佢而跳唔到stage."},{"pid":"ff53b259654d0bea6bb8ecf82e0edeab4dc217b7","tid":780262,"uid":30006,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:48:22.000Z","msg":"22"},{"pid":"9e8f91e272cc3f6dae5772170c1670e5f4acd61f","tid":780262,"uid":73,"like":128,"dislike":6,"score":122,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:51:26.000Z","msg":"當年quit u 慳左3年,<br />\n而家早你個時間表5年"},{"pid":"dc2c1fc3cda694c35142b12a5dae385c18321b00","tid":780262,"uid":30006,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9e8f91e272cc3f6dae5772170c1670e5f4acd61f","tid":780262,"uid":73,"like":128,"dislike":6,"score":122,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:51:26.000Z","msg":"當年quit u 慳左3年,<br />\n而家早你個時間表5年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:52:03.000Z","msg":"叻仔，其實我寫得好保守的了"},{"pid":"064740745e4cd00dffc435b8b55d7df7f25cf08a","tid":780262,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:53:13.000Z","msg":"24歲入左政府hea工<br />\n仲有無發圍機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee6e997dfb358cb5c023d43f3d77166a5f8b9ba","tid":780262,"uid":177089,"like":24,"dislike":4,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"064740745e4cd00dffc435b8b55d7df7f25cf08a","tid":780262,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:53:13.000Z","msg":"24歲入左政府hea工<br />\n仲有無發圍機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:53:49.000Z","msg":"aco? 讓返個位出嚟"},{"pid":"89cd91f5f75f7684f1c3459d588d13429994ddbe","tid":780262,"uid":30006,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"064740745e4cd00dffc435b8b55d7df7f25cf08a","tid":780262,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:53:13.000Z","msg":"24歲入左政府hea工<br />\n仲有無發圍機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:57:07.000Z","msg":"我以前都做過, 人工高，半hae (但要忙真係堅忙) <br />\n<br />\n政府工特色，做死下面肥上面<br />\n<br />\n你要睇下上面d 老屎忽睇唔睇你，如果唔係你跳到 max point 之後就玩完。<br />\n<br />\n如果你有40-50K ，可以儲下錢等時機成熟攪其他野<br />\n<br />\n如果under 20K，hae左成年都無進展，早走早著"},{"pid":"ffb29b18220691ae816d3d9827c27df0baba956c","tid":780262,"uid":20908,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:01:45.000Z","msg":"好撚悲哀<br />\n香港9成男人都係咁既模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ea71c52cc039ad236bff9c81077fb34a02f888","tid":780262,"uid":30006,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ffb29b18220691ae816d3d9827c27df0baba956c","tid":780262,"uid":20908,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:01:45.000Z","msg":"好撚悲哀<br />\n香港9成男人都係咁既模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:08:18.000Z","msg":"咁又唔算慘 <br />\n<br />\n其實發達國家都應該係咁上下"},{"pid":"06ac3f5b1c001c3ce2fcaea9d83a2a74426b43e7","tid":780262,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=